additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: People suffering from perfume sensitivity should be cautious when using this product. Air fresheners do not replace good hygiene practices. May cause an allergic reaction in some individuals. Use only as directed in well ventilated areas. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Always switch off at the socket before removing or inserting the fragrance refill. Do not place in an area where the diffuser may be susceptible to hard knocks. Always keep the bottle and diffuser in an upright position. For indoor use only. Do not operate with wet hands or metal objects.
